author: breser
msg: Fix the _SWIG_TYPE macro and use it in a place it wouldn't work before.
* subversion/bindings/swig/perl/libsvn_swig_perl/swigutil_pl.c
(_SWIG_TYPE): Don't use sizeof() because that restricts it to using
only string constants and also causes it to reference the parameter
more than once which can cause mysterious behavior if the caller
doesn't know about these things and isn't really careful.
(svn_swig_pl_objs_to_hash_by_name): use _SWIG_TYPE() macro instead of
calling _swig_perl_type_query().
